</span><span class="lnt">5
</span><span class="lnt">6
</span><span class="lnt">7
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-markdown" data-lang="markdown"><span class="line"><span class="cl">+++
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">title = &#39;RoboMaster Meta战队&#39;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">subtitle = &#39;2024电控教学主页&#39;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">date = 2024-05-14T14:17:45-05:00
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">draft = false
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">url = &#39;/meta-teaching/main&#39;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">+++</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p>该静态页面就会显示在网站/meta-teaching/main页面。</p>
